  "instructions": [
    "In a small bowl, mix yeast, pomegranate molasses, and 1/4 cup water to create the starter.",
    "Add the starter to the squid and marinate for at least 2 hours.",
    "Heat the olive oil in a large cazuela over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Add the cumin, coriander, and red pepper flakes and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the squid to the cazuela and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the yeast mixture and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the stew to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with parsley if desired."
